1
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:07,500
♪That dangerous temptation♪

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,020
♪Like a whirlpool churning deep♪

3
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:12,900
♪Like a moth darts into the flame♪

4
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:14,340
♪Falling towards the light♪

5
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:17,420
♪Watch as everything drowns in shadows♪

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,340
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

7
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:23,220
♪See the blazing sparks ignite♪

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,060
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,460
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,820
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
00:00:32,060 --> 00:00:34,850
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

12
00:00:34,850 --> 00:00:37,820
[Miss Mystery]

13
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:41,240
As expected,
the only one who can find it is you,

14
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,320
Xue Tong.

15
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:43,360
Long,

16
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:45,240
tie them both up!

17
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:45,840
Yes!

18
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,480
What are you looking at?

19
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:48,840
Kill me if you can.

20
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,080
You are my son. How can I kill you?

21
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:54,320
You are just like your father,

22
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,120
not cherishing opportunities.

23
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,600
Son,

24
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:01,160
only by this woman dying before you

25
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,320
can you understand

26
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,000
my good intentions and love for you.

27
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:07,140
[Episode 24]

28
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,280
Son,

29
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:12,280
only by this woman dying before you

30
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,880
can you understand
my good intentions and love for you.

31
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:15,480
No!

32
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,560
Zhu Mao,

33
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,440
don't kill her!

34
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,320
You killed my mom before,

35
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,280
and if you kill her,

36
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,240
I won't spare you even in hell!

37
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,320
I didn't kill your mom!

38
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,600
She tripped and fell!

39
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:35,520
Everything I have done was for Peiqin!

40
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:39,800
I fell in love with her at first sight,

41
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,640
long before Zhou Jishu even met her.

42
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:46,800
It's just that back then,
I was a poor guy,

43
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,240
and I wasn't good enough for her.

44
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,760
But now, I've made it.

45
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,560
I've become wealthy.

46
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,720
I didn't mind
that she'd been married before,

47
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,680
and I was even willing

48
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,440
to treat her child as my own.

49
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,560
But what about her?

50
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,320
This damn woman...

51
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,560
I've done so much,

52
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,880
and she couldn't even see it.

53
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,240
Instead, she wanted to expose my doings.

54
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,520
You should know

55
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,600
that it's because of me

56
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:19,800
that you all could live a life
of luxury.

57
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,880
I did all these things,
and she still didn't understand me

58
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,440
or appreciate my efforts.

59
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,080
If I didn't kill her,

60
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,280
the dead one would be me!

61
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,080
Long!

62
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,320
How is this possible?

63
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:57,320
This big brute.
I thought he was impressive.

64
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,520
Who are you?

65
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:03,920
I can find all the answers;

66
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,320
I am Bai Xiaosheng.

67
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,400
If I don't leave the Zhu manor tonight,

68
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,960
call this number.

69
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,000
Mrs. Zhu,

70
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,040
look who is here!

71
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,480
Master Zhu,

72
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,040
your truck of goods

73
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,080
all went back to their homes.

74
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,520
It seems
that your distinguished face

75
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,040
will be on the front page headlines
of tomorrow's newspaper.

76
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,200
Spare your empty threats.

77
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,800
I'm the most powerful...

78
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,160
This bullet

79
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,720
is for Guanwen.

80
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,440
This bullet

81
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,960
is for all the lives you've harmed.

82
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,200
This bullet

83
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,680
is for all the Chinese people
you've sold to Southeast Asia.

84
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,160
It's their destiny.

85
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,720
My life

86
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,480
is more valuable than theirs!

87
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,600
This bullet

88
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,920
is for my parents.

89
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:16,700
[Tombs of Zhu Guanwen
and Lin Bao'er's Parents]

90
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,960
Dad, Mom,

91
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,840
Xue Tong is back to see you.

92
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,720
Dad,

93
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,480
Mom,

94
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,760
I'm here to see you.

95
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,600
This is my fiance,

96
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,960
Guanwen.

97
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:48,920
This woman

98
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,120
is my fiancee

99
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,680
and your daughter-in-law,

100
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:54,760
Xue Tong.

101
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,720
Rest in peace.

102
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,480
We will live a good life.

103
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,760
Let's go.

104
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,600
Are you in a bad mood?

105
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:25,960
No.

106
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:27,600
How about this?

107
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,680
I have something for you.

108
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,600
Guess what it is.

109
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:52,600
Guanwen,

110
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:55,040
do you want to have

111
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,720
a unique wedding with me?

112
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,560
Are you

113
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,120
proposing to me?

114
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,160
Silly!

115
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:17,960
Look!

116
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:28,780
♪It seems to be changing♪

117
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:32,380
♪The familiar yet strange face♪

118
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:34,620
♪I want to get close♪

119
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:38,140
♪To those once bright eyes♪

120
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:41,420
♪So far away♪

121
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:44,260
♪Unable to touch♪

122
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:47,900
♪Between us♪

123
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,680
I think I saw my parents.

124
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,240
I saw them, too.

125
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,640
I also promised them

126
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,200
to take good care of you.

127
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:03,620
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

128
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:07,820
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

129
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,440
(Guanwen,)

130
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,800
(I thought that the fire
from 18 years ago)

131
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,910
(had burnt away all my emotions)

132
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:20,320
(except my love for family.)

133
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,480
(But ever since I met you
in Lianhe Town,)

134
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:28,080
(you have unconditionally trusted
and helped me.)

135
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:29,840
For my whole life,

136
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,880
I will always protect you.

137
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,320
If your next target is the mayor,

138
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:35,720
I'll be here for you.

139
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,320
You are not alone now.

140
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,560
You still have me.

141
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,160
I only know one thing:

142
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,360
I want to be by your side

143
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,760
and face everything together with you.

144
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,720
I won't stop you
from doing what you want,

145
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:50,000
but I will do it with you.

146
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:55,480
(You have lit up my world once again,)

147
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,600
(much like that ray of light
from 18 years ago.)

148
00:08:58,940 --> 00:09:01,020
♪I may reopen my eyes♪

149
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,280
(Now,)

150
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,880
(what the candy has brought to me
is not just comfort)

151
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,560
(but also the courage
coming from having you by my side.)

152
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,400
(So, Guanwen,)

153
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:17,480
(I wholeheartedly want to marry you.)

154
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:21,960
(Let's be together forever,)

155
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,640
(never to part.)

156
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:28,500
♪The end has now been reached♪

157
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:31,420
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

158
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,740
♪Looking away from you♪

159
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:38,860
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

160
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:43,060
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

161
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:49,700
[The end]

162
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:53,420
♪The end has now been reached♪

163
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,340
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

164
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:59,620
♪Looking away from you♪

165
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:03,780
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

166
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:07,220
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

167
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:12,260
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

168
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:18,880
♪In a moment♪

169
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,760
♪Flitting images flashing♪

170
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:24,140
♪Eyes fall shut♪

171
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:27,980
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

172
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,360
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

173
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,280
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

174
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:39,560
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

175
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:43,700
♪In a moment♪

176
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:46,620
♪The memory in my mind♪

177
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:48,540
♪Surging at me♪

178
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:52,900
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

179
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:56,020
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

180
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:59,180
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

181
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:02,540
♪I may reopen my eyes♪
